title: 11 September 2015: Contemporary Conversations with Eric Fischl (Embassy of the United States - Ottawa, ...
text: ( Source : Embassy of the United States - Ottawa, Canada ) Ambassador Heyman interviews artist Eric Fischl in the National Gallery of Canada . Why painting, and why now? Those questions, as well as many others, were the topics of conversation
